{"tid":1945552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【仆街YMCA 隱瞞酒店有確診患者】","createTime":"2020-03-27T06:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T17:23:19.000Z","uid":345716,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a025d57698dcf7c8c518db0b926647a7e1ef56c7","tid":1945552,"uid":345716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"利申：前YMCA 員工，歡迎追翻之前啲po<br />\n有現職員工想我幫手出PO<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有肺炎確診患者曾經入住YMCA 1537號房，如果冇乜事唔好出入YMCA，請轉告身邊的朋友</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n藍高層想隱瞞，側側膊想過骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班高層由今朝到依家乜嘢聲氣都未有，冇通報所有員工或公眾，連個出個Facebook Post 都懶，妄顧所有員工、會員、住客、客户性命。<br />\n<br />\n你班藍高層，依家仲擺商譽前過人命<br />\n<br />\n屌那媽，員工屋企有大有細，累到人你就仆街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>利申：暫時未有source，但小心為上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n有時間去Google Review/FB 寫鳩佢啲惡行，俾啲壓力班高層出黎承認事件。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ymcahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fymcahk%2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=1c6e1007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ymcahk/</a>"},{"pid":"09b26b8ecfc70070755f22d748425ced622e6205","tid":1945552,"uid":88740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:48:05.000Z","msg":"咁仆街都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56212e9fa7f7c6a72c988b3318761998bcc9ba5a","tid":1945552,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:49:21.000Z","msg":"ymca 呢輪真係多醜聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0fae94